pos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/whats-app-end-to-end-encryption-for-backups-150954934.html">端到端加密的</a>保护，如果一小时内没有人活跃，语音聊天也会被关闭。 WhatsApp 语音聊天目前似乎仅针对 Android 用户提供测试版，但据称未来几天将向更多用户开放。</p><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/whatsapps-latest-feature-lets-you-jump-in-and-out-of-group-voice-chats-121045597.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/whatsapps-latest-feature-lets-you-jump-in-and-out-of-group-voice-chats-121045597.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> caf39793-3856-49b0-adab-21f80eceadba</guid><dc:creator>萨拉·菲尔丁</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Mon, 07 Aug 2023 12:10:45 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691408874</ingested><modified> 2023-08-07T11:48:10+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Small Businesses]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Sarah Fielding]]></category><media:content height="3334" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/3ad713c0-20b4-11ee-bdff-de6f16b6493a" width="5000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3334" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/3ad713c0-20b4-11ee-bdff-de6f16b6493a" width="5000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[SOPA Images via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:desc