epression-pill-063216439.html">FDA 批准首个口服产后抑郁药</a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/coinbase-wants-its-sec-lawsuit-dismissed-arguing-it-doesnt-deal-in-securities-170056685.html">Coinbase 希望美国证券交易委员会驳回诉讼，称其不从事证券交易</a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/gamestops-nft-wallet-will-shut-down-in-november-164252057.html">GameStop 的 NFT 钱包将于 11 月关闭</a></p><h2></h2><h2><a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/call-of-duty-is-publicly-shaming-cheaters-in-the-kill-feed-154544553.html">《使命召唤》在杀戮动态中公开羞辱作弊者</a></h2><h3>如果您被发现使用漏洞，您将被点名并受到羞辱。</h3><p></p><p>我不喜欢那种快来命名和羞耻的文化——我们都在参加同样的比赛，但背负着不同重量的行李。但动视认为，对于那些在后台运行作弊软件的在线玩《使命召唤》的人来说，有一个例外。 Ricochet反作弊系统的最新更新将<a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/call-of-duty-is-publicly-shaming-cheaters-in-the-kill-feed-154544553.html">检测到不公平游戏的用户</a>，将他们从游戏中引导出来，并让每个人都知道他们一直在与作弊者打交道。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/call-of-duty-is-publicly-shaming-cheaters-in-the-kill-feed-154544553.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a></p><h2> <a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/a-2490-wireless-podcasting-kit-is-absurd-but-at-least-nomonos-sounds-great-140053574.html">2,490 美元的无线播客套件很荒谬，但至少 Nomono 的听起来很棒</a></h2><h3>这是一个包装精美的一体化工作室，但是……你知道。</h3> <a href="https://www.engadget.com/a-2490-wireless-podcasting-kit-is-absurd-but-at-least-nomonos-sounds-great-140053574.html"><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/51eab930-3505-11ee-babf-452ad0b81285" style="height:395px;width:625px;" alt="Nomono 一体化播客工作室的图片，位于白色门前的深色木桌上。" data-uuid="946e3f8f-70b3-353d-b28e-8b964b30df82"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">摄影：Devindra Hardawar / Engadget</div></figure></a><p> Nomono 的<a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/a-2490-wireless-podcasting-kit-is-absurd-but-at-least-nomonos-sounds-great-140053574.html">一体化播客工作室</a>拥有一系列足够长的功能，足以让 Devindra Hardawar 花时间使用它。只需 2